Properties account?

25:35.417 --> 25:36.959
Well, I can forge it.

25:36.960 --> 25:38.795
Do you want me to forge it?

25:38.796 --> 25:41.089
You're a criminal.

25:43.634 --> 25:45.760
- Alright, let's go.
- Hey.

25:45.761 --> 25:48.096
Bye, guys! Thank you!

25:48.097 --> 25:50.081
- Hi.
- Thank God you're open.

25:50.082 --> 25:51.841
- Only one in the neighborhood.
- Two, three... You know what?

25:51.842 --> 25:53.226
We can squeeze you in this way.

25:53.227 --> 25:55.520
Oh. Uh... we're not with them.

25:55.521 --> 25:56.897
Well, you are now. Follow me.

25:56.898 --> 25:58.273
Impromptu tonight.

25:58.274 --> 26:00.609
No power, our chef is
cooking up a storm.

26:00.610 --> 26:02.193
You'll see. Have a seat.

26:02.194 --> 26:04.237
Do you guys mind a little company?

26:04.238 --> 26:06.072
We can put the tables
together. Thank you.

26:06.073 --> 26:08.241
Gina, can you help me with the table?

26:08.242 --> 26:09.659
Oh, yes. Yes.

26:09.660 --> 26:11.912
Oh, yeah. Thank you. Mm-hmm.

26:15.750 --> 26:17.000
You wanted a sign?

26:17.001 --> 26:19.128
- I think you just got one.
- I think so, too.

26:19.129 --> 26:20.930
- Here we go. This is our chef.
- Hi.

26:20.931 --> 26:22.898
- Please sit down, everyone.
- Everyone, dig in.

26:22.899 --> 26:25.134
- How long we got to be in here?
- As long as it takes.

26:25.135 --> 26:27.302
Unless, of course, you want
to use the snot sucker.

26:26.803 --> 26:29.013
- The snot sucker?
- It's exactly what it sounds like,

26:29.014 --> 26:30.264
except you use your mouth.

26:30.265 --> 26:31.807
Steam shower it is.

26:33.685 --> 26:36.520
There you go, Charlie.

26:36.521 --> 26:38.856
There you go, baby.

26:38.357 --> 26:41.016
- Hey, um... sorry about earlier.
- Oh, no, no.

26:41.041 --> 26:42.801
- Dude, dude, dude...
- I shouldn't have...

26:42.825 --> 26:44.028
...I can't even imagine

26:44.029 --> 26:45.948
what that must feel like for you, man.

26:47.324 --> 26:48.992
You hear that?

26:48.993 --> 26:50.743
What?

26:50.744 --> 26:52.328
Exactly.

26:52.329 --> 26:54.581
Silence.

26:54.082 --> 26:57.501
You knew exactly what to do
to take care of your daughter.

26:57.502 --> 26:59.378
Thanks.

26:59.379 --> 27:03.215
But all I can think about
is how in two hours,

27:03.216 --> 27:05.592
I have to walk out that front door.

27:05.093 --> 27:08.470
You know, I missed the first
three months of Theo's life

27:08.471 --> 27:10.890
'cause I was in rehab.

27:10.891 --> 27:12.850
And now I'm here,

27:12.851 --> 27:16.270
and I know exactly what I'm missing.

27:16.271 --> 27:17.855
And it kills me.

27:18.941 --> 27:20.066
It's okay.

27:20.067 --> 27:21.609
There you go.

27:21.610 --> 27:23.736
It's okay.

27:23.737 --> 27:26.280
She was always closer to Chad.

27:26.281 --> 27:28.574
They had this connection...

27:28.575 --> 27:34.080
that she never really had with me.

27:33.581 --> 27:35.415
Maybe she was closer with your brother,

27:35.416 --> 27:37.542
but it doesn't mean she...

27:37.543 --> 27:39.502
doesn't care about you.

27:39.503 --> 27:42.130
I get that you're trying
to make me feel better,

27:42.131 --> 27:43.256
but trust me.

27:43.257 --> 27:44.674
I know what I'm talking about.

27:47.053 --> 27:49.346
Well, you should know

27:49.347 --> 27:52.557
that the first time she wrote me was...

27:52.558 --> 27:54.809
right after you got sick.

27:57.313 --> 28:01.191
In fact, the only reason
she reached out to me

28:00.692 --> 28:04.486
is because she was
terrified of losing you.

28:05.864 --> 28:08.824
That's what she wrote in her letter.

28:11.078 --> 28:12.912
Grief...

28:12.913 --> 28:17.041
has a way of making
people do crazy things.

